      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MILO DAVIS (7) has a strong overall record having 22 wins and 29 places from 75 starts but was out of the money last time when fourth (20.08) over 352m at Q Lakeside. Has never been out of the money in six starts this course and distance. Has the ability and looks a key chance this line-up. ROSEWOOD REBEL (6) has mixed form, but did hit the frame three back and was narrowly beaten next start before a sixth (19.47) at this track in a Mix 5 latest. Can hit the frame this time. JAGGER'S JAM (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Whiskey My Way (19.55) in a Mix 5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Leading player again. PROFESSOR NESSA (2) looks an each-way chance.",
